                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On January 14, 1952, President <persName corresp="#p_THS1">Truman</persName>
                    announced that General <persName>Clark</persName>’s nomination as Ambassador to
                    the State of Vatican City was being withdrawn at <persName>Clark</persName>’s
                    request. Documentation pertaining to this announcement, as well as to the
                    subsequent consideration within the United States Government of the possible
                    establishment of diplomatic relations with the Vatican, is scheduled for
                    publication in <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1952-1954, volume
                    VI.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
